# Applications Directory

Track job applications here.

Structure:
```
data/applications/
├── 2025/
│   ├── active.json           # Currently applying/interviewing
│   ├── completed.json        # Final outcomes (offer/rejected/ghosted)
│   └── january-archive.json  # Monthly archive
└── templates/
    └── cover-letters/
```

Status flow:
`new → applied → phone_screen → interview → offer → hired`
`new → applied → rejected`
`new → applied → ghosted` (no response > 30 days)
